  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0dcf\u0dc3\u0dca\u0d9a\u0dd4 \u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dc4\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dba \u0d9c\u0dd0\u0db1 \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dc1\u0db1\u0dba \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd3\u0db8\u0da7 \u0db1\u0dcf\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dba\u0db1\u0dca \u0d85\u0d9a\u0db8\u0dd0\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0d87\u0dba\u0dd2?",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Why do leaders not want to investigate the Easter attack?",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Malcolm Cardinal Ranjith, the Archbishop of Colombo, said that there is a doubt whether the leaders of the country do not want to investigate the terrorist attack on Easter Sunday, because their participation in it will be revealed.",
        "The Archbishops of Colombo said that there must be some secret here, and if the leaders are honest and not involved, they should not be afraid of investigation.",
        "Malcolm Cardinal Ranjith, the Archbishop of Colombo, said this while participating in the blessing service held today (21) at the Tewatta Basilica Church, Ragama.",
        "The Cardinals also said that even though it has been 40 months since the Easter attack, justice has not yet been served.",
        "The Archbishop of Colombo who said that life becomes dark because of patrimonial desires, also said that success does not mean winning wealth and power.",
        "Malcolm Cardinal Ranjith and the Archbishop of Colombo said that selfishness and sin have been reigning in the country for 75 years from the recent unfortunate events in the country.",
        "When a group of leaders who came to power ruled by saying that they would create a righteous society, the country's social system was created, when they said that a miracle would be done in Asia, a big tower was built, and when there was prosperity, the archbishops who said that six million people had only one meal to eat, those systems changed. They also stated that"
      ],
